agentData.mission: Produce a concise, actionable mission spec that translates the high-level goal into a short operational plan for specialist teams (researchers, developers, archivists). The spec should identify required outputs (protocol checklist, metadata standard, lightweight plugins), target evaluation methods (surveys, audit studies), key stakeholders (journals, archives, PsychClassics/Project Gutenberg maintainers), and an initial rollout & validation timeline.
